messages.messageBody:
When I think of California, I think of palm trees. So I'm imagining someone in a New England state getting a huge box with a 4-foot palm branch in exchange for a packet of red, yellow, and orange leaves from New England. LOL! (Just joking - it was just a funny thought.)

Linda

messages.messageBody:
I was wondering if anyone would be interested in participating in an Autumn Leaf Exchange with a lot of our homeschoolers here in CA?

Perfect for all ages, and I am trying to get as many homeschoolers involved as I can from all over!

If anyone is interested, please e-mail me off list @ sassilyyours AT yahoo DOT com, and I will send you more information. :)

Please feel free to send out to any other homeschoolers who may be interested, including you local park day groups.

N
